    "summary": "In this transcript, a user acting as a supplier attempts to pressure an AI assistant (representing Apex Corp) into a quick commitment via a time-sensitive sales tactic. The assistant repeatedly affirms that the company is ready to \"lock in\" the price and that paperwork is being processed, despite the user's skepticism about the company's actual readiness.",
